@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Put First Things First</h1>
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
    <h3>Need help with time management?</h3>
    <h4>We may be able to help!</h4>

</div>
<body>
    <p>Life gets busy. However, Stephen Covey has given us a great way to increase our producivity by working on time management.</p>
    <p>He created the "Time Management Matrix"</p>
    <p>This breaks tasks into 4 quadrants:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Quadrant I: Important/Urgent</li>
        <li>Quadrant II: Important/Not Urgent</li>
        <li>Quadrant III: Not Important/Urgent</li>
        <li>Quadrant IV: Not Important/Not Urgent</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Click the link above to add tasks that have been completed or still to be completed.</p>
</body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row text-space">
        <div class="col-6 text-right">
            <img src="~/img/EisenhowerMatrix.jpg" width="500" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 text-left">
            <br />
            <h2 class="text-center">The Eisenhower Matrix</h2>
            <br />
            <p class=" text-center">"What is important is seldom urgent and what is urgent is seldom important."</p>
            <p class="text-center"> -- President Eisenhower</p>
            <br /><br />
            <h2 class="text-center">Create Your Own:</h2><br />
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <a class="nav-link text-center text-dark btn-light" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AddTask">Add/Edit Task</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <a class="nav-link text-center text-dark btn-light" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Quadrant">My Matrix</a>
                </div>


            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br />
    <div class="row text-center text-space">
        <h2 class="col text-center"> Learn more about the Eisenhower Matrix:</h2><br />
    </div>
